{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/warung-ichiraku-ramen-naruto-di-dunia-nyata/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Warung “Ichiraku Ramen” Naruto Di Dunia Nyata!","content":"<p>Sebuah tempat atau bangunan asli dengan lokasi dunia nyata sudah sering dijadikan objek dalam sebuah cerita manga atau komik. Ada banyak alasan untuk itu. Seperti misalnya sebagai penegasan lokasi dari cerita yang ada (ambil contoh komik Spider-Man yang mengambil lokasi asli Queens di Manhattan, Amerika Serikat). Kemudian ada pula lokasi asli yang kemudian di-fiksi-kan dengan cara mengganti nama; seperti kota fiksi Smallville di komik Superman, yang terletak di Kansas. Kansas sendiri merupakan lokasi asli di Amerika Serikat.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47361\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47361\" data-attachment-id=\"47361\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/proteksi-bajakan-nintendo-switch-bobol/attachment/ichira7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ichira7\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Lokasi fiksi di daerah asli. (Sumber: Wikia)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47361\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47361\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lokasi fiksi di daerah asli. (Sumber: Wikia)</p></div></p>\n<p>Juga ada situasi dimana seorang pengarang komik atau manga terinspirasi pada satu aspek di sebuah kota/lokasi dan menggunakannya sebagai bagian dari manga/komik yang sedang dia kerjakan.</p>\n<p>Ambil contoh mangaka Tsukasa Hojo yang sering menggunakan lokasi asli “Kabuki-cho” di Shinjuku, Tokyo Jepang sebagai lokasi reguler manga “City Hunter” ciptaannya. Hal ini lumrah terjadi dan bukan sesuatu yang tidak biasa dilakukan oleh mangaka Jepang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47360\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47360\" data-attachment-id=\"47360\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/proteksi-bajakan-nintendo-switch-bobol/attachment/ichira6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ichira6\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Shinjuku, Tokyo. (Sumber: JPNInfo)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47360\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47360\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Shinjuku, Tokyo. (Sumber: JPNInfo)</p></div></p>\n<p>Mangaka Jepang Masashi Kishimoto yang dikenal luas sebagai pencipta manga fenomenal “Naruto” juga melakukan hal ini.</p>\n<p>Menghibur jutaan fans sejak rilis pertama di majalah komik Weekly Shonen Jump di tahun 1999, Naruto tidak pernah benar-benar ‘berhenti’ sejak ditamatkan oleh Kishimoto-sensei tahun 2014. “<a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/teori-teori-internet-seputar-kematian-naruto-di-boruto-naruto-next-generation/\">Boruto</a>” merupakan sekuel langsung dari Naruto, dan sepertinya diterima pasar dengan baik. Produk-produk turunan manga Naruto seperti <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/naruto-shippuden-ultimate-ninja-storm-trilogy-yang-dibuat-untuk-nintendo-switch/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">video game </a>juga tidak berhenti dirilis selepas tamatnya manga Naruto.</p>\n<p>Intinya? Naruto tidak (akan) mati dan mungkin hidup panjang seperti <em>franchise</em> manga populer lain.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47367\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47367\" data-attachment-id=\"47367\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/proteksi-bajakan-nintendo-switch-bobol/attachment/tomb2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/tomb2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"tomb2\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: Gamer.NL)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/tomb2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/tomb2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47367\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/tomb2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/tomb2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/tomb2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47367\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: Gamer.NL)</p></div></p>\n<p><em>Fans</em> Naruto tentu tahu dengan satu lokasi penting dan jadi <em>signature</em> di manga serta anime Naruto, yaitu warung mie “Ichiraku Ramen”. Tempat ini termasuk penting di manga Naruto; buku tankobon Naruto volume 16 bahkan memakai warung ini sebagai cover!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47358\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47358\" data-attachment-id=\"47358\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/proteksi-bajakan-nintendo-switch-bobol/attachment/ichira4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ichira4\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Lokasi nongkrong karakter manga Naruto. (Sumber: SoraNews24)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47358\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47358\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lokasi nongkrong karakter manga Naruto. (Sumber: SoraNews24)</p></div></p>\n<p><em>Fans</em> tentu tahu kalau makanan kesukaan Naruto di manga itu adalah ramen dari warung Ichiraku Ramen. Tapi mungkin fans belum tahu kalau warung itu ada di dunia nyata dan Masashi Kishimoto terinspirasi dengan tempat tersebut hingga menciptakan versinya sendiri di manga Naruto.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47356\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47356\" data-attachment-id=\"47356\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/proteksi-bajakan-nintendo-switch-bobol/attachment/ichira2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ichira2\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Visualisasi Ichiraku Ramen versi Masashi Kishimoto. (Sumber: Allabout-Japan)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47356\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47356\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Visualisasi Ichiraku Ramen versi Masashi Kishimoto. (Sumber: Allabout-Japan)</p></div></p>\n<p>Masashi Kishimoto menggunakan model warung ramen di Kyuusandaimae, Fukuoka Jepang. Saat masa-masa bersekolah dulu, dia sering melewati dan mampir di warung ramen Kyuusandaimae tersebut. Hal itu jadi inspirasinya saat menciptakan Ichiraku Ramen di Konoha. Tapi sayang warung ramen Kyuusandaimae tersebut tutup di tahun 2014.</p>\n<p>Persis di tahun Naruto ditamatkan. Kebetulan atau tidak? Entahlah.</p>\n<p>Walau tutup toko di Kyuusandaimae tapi warung tersebut ternyata punya cabang di lokasi lain Fukuoka; salah satunya tepat di Shime (dekat <em>airport</em> Fukuoka). Ternyata warung tersebut termasuk laris, karena orang-orang sudah pada antri bahkan sebelum pintu warung dibuka.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47357\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47357\" data-attachment-id=\"47357\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/proteksi-bajakan-nintendo-switch-bobol/attachment/ichira3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ichira3\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tampilan depan warung ramen inspirasi Kishimoto-sensei. (Sumber: TripAdvisor)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47357\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47357\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tampilan depan warung ramen inspirasi Kishimoto-sensei. (Sumber: TripAdvisor)</p></div></p>\n<p>Pilihan menu ada beberapa jenis namun karena Naruto penggemar ramen dengan miso maka yang dipesan adalah ramen dengan miso. Semangkuk Miso Chashu Pork Ramen dihargai 850 Yen atau US$ 8,48 (sekitar IDR 118rb). Lumayan jika melihat besarnya porsi yang diberikan dengan harga segitu.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47359\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47359\" data-attachment-id=\"47359\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/proteksi-bajakan-nintendo-switch-bobol/attachment/ichira5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ichira5\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Ukuran jumbo dengan topping melimpah. (Sumber: SoraNews24)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47359\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47359\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ukuran jumbo dengan topping melimpah. (Sumber: SoraNews24)</p></div></p>\n<p>Miso Chashu Pork Ramen dihidangkan dalam wadah mangkuk berukuran besar. <em>Topping</em> atas dari ramen terlihat berupa tauge, cabe hijau serta irisan chashu pork alias daging babi berukuran jumbo. Kuah kaldunya walau terasa ringan namun cukup ‘nonjok’. Paduan mie ramen lembut dan irisan daging tebal menjadikan hidangan ramen seperti yang dinikmati Naruto di manga terasa sedap sekali menurut yang sudah pernah mencobanya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47355\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47355\" data-attachment-id=\"47355\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/proteksi-bajakan-nintendo-switch-bobol/attachment/ichira1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ichira1\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Irisan daging pork ukuran gede. (Sumber: SoraNews24)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47355\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ichira1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47355\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Irisan daging <em>pork</em> ukuran gede. (Sumber: SoraNews24)</p></div></p>\n<p>Dengan harga ideal, rasa nikmat serta ukuran porsi yang mengenyangkan, ramen khas Ichiraku Ramen dari manga Naruto bisa dinikmati di dunia nyata. Sayang karena non-halal maka sepertinya ramen ini tidak direkomendasikan untuk mereka yang dilarang mengonsumsi daging babi. Namun untuk yang tidak punya masalah dengan konsumsi daging babi, <em>go ahead</em> <em>ttebayo!</em></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"241bb410-6df4-5a85-b984-b3ea6da11fc7"}}}